tool_description: Europa League Live Scores API allows to retrieve current season results, scorers, lineups, substitutes, events, statistics and much more all with live updates, for EUFA Europa League. And more is coming...
name: Europa League Live Scores
title: Europa League Live Scores

api_list.name: Group Table
api_list.description: Returns the table for a group

optional_parameters.name: time
optional_parameters.description: Let to compute the table considering only the first half (FH) or the second time (SH) results. Default is full time (FT).

api_list.name: Bookmakers List
api_list.description: Returns the list of the available bookmakers for a match

api_list.name: Match statistics

optional_parameters.name: live
optional_parameters.description: Returns data for a playing match (default false)

optional_parameters.name: matchday
optional_parameters.description: Match day number for the match

api_list.name: Matches results
api_list.description: Returns all matches for a specified match day number

optional_parameters.name: live
optional_parameters.description: Returns matches and results with live updates (default false)

optional_parameters.name: date
optional_parameters.description: Return matches in the date (format mmddyyyy).

optional_parameters.name: group
optional_parameters.description: Group code (A..K). Mandatory for 1<=matchday<=6

optional_parameters.name: matchday
optional_parameters.description: Match day number

api_list.name: Player stats for a match
api_list.description: Returns the player's statistics for a match

optional_parameters.name: matchday
optional_parameters.description: Match day number for the match

api_list.name: Lineups and substitutes for a match
api_list.description: Returns lineups, substitutes and coaches for a game (only after the game is finished).

optional_parameters.name: live
optional_parameters.description: Returns data for a playing match (default false)

optional_parameters.name: matchday
optional_parameters.description: Match day number for the match

api_list.name: Missing players for a match
api_list.description: Return all the players who will miss the match and the reason

optional_parameters.name: matchday
optional_parameters.description: Match day number for the match

api_list.name: Odds List
api_list.description: Returns the available odds for a match and a bookmaker

api_list.name: Match scorers
api_list.description: Returns when and how the scorers scored in a match

optional_parameters.name: live
optional_parameters.description: Returns data for a playing match (default false)

optional_parameters.name: matchday
optional_parameters.description: Match day number for the match

api_list.name: Top scorers
api_list.description: Returns top scorers for the Cup or the number of goals scored by a player

optional_parameters.name: fromdate
optional_parameters.description: Compute the table only with matches played format (format mmddyyyy)

optional_parameters.name: todate
optional_parameters.description: Compute the table only with matches played todate (format mmddyyyy)

optional_parameters.name: page
optional_parameters.description: Page result to return. Default is 1 that are results from 1 to 5 (max. value is 20).

optional_parameters.name: player
optional_parameters.description: Player name

optional_parameters.name: team
optional_parameters.description: Team name

api_list.name: Match events
api_list.description: Returns all the events for a match

optional_parameters.name: live
optional_parameters.description: Returns data for a playing match (default false)

optional_parameters.name: matchday
optional_parameters.description: Match day number for the match

api_list.name: Odd quotas
api_list.description: Returns quotas for an odd a match and a bookmaker
